[6 common discord scams (video)](<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Jz-3goOPj9o>) <:zwinterwumpus_sip:1143956675766796360> 

By staying informed and cautious, we can keep ourselves and all communities safe from these threats.

Stay safe, everyone!
